file.name: distance-targeting.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  title: Adzerk Management API - Distance Targeting
  description: Advertiser related Adzerk Management API
  version: '1.0'
servers:
  - url: 'https://api.adzerk.net'
tags:
  - name: distance-target
    description: Manage Distance Targeting
paths:
  '/v1/flight/{flightId}/distance':
    post:
      tags:
        - distance-targeting
      operationId: create
      security:
        - ApiKeyAuth: []
      parameters:
        - name: flightId
          description: The Flight Id to associate with the Distance Targeting geometry object
          in: path
          required: true
          schema:
            type: integer
            format: int32
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: object
              properties:
                Distance:
                  type: integer
                  format: float
                  nullable: true
                Latitude:
                  type: integer
                  format: float
                  nullable: true
                Longitude:
                  type: integer
                  format: float
                  nullable: true
                StreetAddress:
                  type: string
                  nullable: true
      responses:
        400:
          description: Bad Request Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
        503:
          description: Geocoding service unavailable
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
        200:
          description: The newly created Distance Target
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: './schemas/distance-target.yaml#/schemas/DistanceTarget'
    get:
      tags:
        - distance-targeting
      operationId: list
      security:
        - ApiKeyAuth: []
      parameters:
        - name: flightId
          description: The Flight Id to associate with the Distance Targeting geometry object
          in: path
          required: true
          schema:
            type: integer
            format: int32
      responses:
        200:
          description: The successful list of Distance Target geometries
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: array
                items:
                  $ref: './schemas/distance-target.yaml#/schemas/DistanceTarget'
  '/v1/flight/{flightId}/distance/batch':
    post:
      tags:
        - distance-targeting
      operationId: batchUpload
      security:
        - ApiKeyAuth: []
      parameters:
        - name: flightId
          description: The Flight Id to associate with the Distance Targeting geometry object
          in: path
          required: true
          schema:
            type: integer
            format: int32
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: object
              properties:
                ReplaceExisting:
                  type: boolean
                  nullable: true
                Geometries:
                  type: array
                  items: 
                    Distance:
                      type: number
                      format: float
                    Latitude:
                      type: number
                      format: float
                    Longitude:
                      type: number
                      format: float
      responses:
        200:
          description: The newly uploaded Distance Target(s)
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  InsertedGeometries: 
                    type: integer
                    format: int32
  '/v1/flight/{flightId}/distance/{geometryId}':
    put:
      tags:
        - distance-targeting
      operationId: update
      security:
        - ApiKeyAuth: []
      parameters:
        - name: flightId
          description: The Flight Id to associate with the Distance Targeting geometry object
          in: path
          required: true
          schema:
            type: integer
            format: int32
        - name: geometryId
          description: The Id of the Distance Targeting geometry
          in: path
          required: true
          schema:
            type: integer
            format: int32
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: object
              properties:
                Distance:
                  type: integer
                  format: float
                  nullable: true
                Latitude:
                  type: integer
                  format: float
                  nullable: true
                Longitude:
                  type: integer
                  format: float
                  nullable: true
                StreetAddress:
                  type: string
                  nullable: true
      responses:
        400:
          description: Bad Request Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
        503:
          description: Geocoding service unavailable
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
        200:
          description: The updated Distance Target geometry
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: './schemas/distance-target.yaml#/schemas/DistanceTarget'
    get:
      tags:
        - distance-targeting
      operationId: get
      security:
        - ApiKeyAuth: []
      parameters:
        - name: flightId
          description: The Flight Id to associate with the Distance Targeting geometry object
          in: path
          required: true
          schema:
            type: integer
            format: int32
        - name: geometryId
          description: The Id of the Distance Targeting geometry
          in: path
          required: true
          schema:
            type: integer
            format: int32
      responses:
        400:
          description: Bad Request Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
        200:
          description: The successful get Distance Target geometry
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: './schemas/distance-target.yaml#/schemas/DistanceTarget'
    delete:
      tags:
        - distance-targeting
      operationId: delete
      security:
        - ApiKeyAuth: []
      parameters:
        - name: flightId
          description: The Flight Id to associate with the Distance Targeting geometry object
          in: path
          required: true
          schema:
            type: integer
            format: int32
        - name: geometryId
          description: The Id of the Distance Targeting geometry
          in: path
          required: true
          schema:
            type: integer
            format: int32
      responses:
        400:
          description: Bad Request Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
        200:
          description: Successfully deleted
